{"tid":1842242,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"陳淑莊要求立即封閉各個關口　阻止內地旅客入境","createTime":"2020-01-25T14:50:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T15:04:55.000Z","uid":81228,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4dbc6061c53d12fdd279597d3e655f59a68b2b8e","tid":1842242,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"立法會民主派會議召集人陳淑莊說，香港目前正處於關鍵時刻，要求立即封閉各個關口，阻止內地旅客入境，又建議政府為從內地回港的市民設特別通道作體溫檢測。<br />\n<br />\n議會陣線朱凱廸說，內地疫情嚴重，批評政府推出多項措施，但迴避將香港與內地分隔，是「將頭埋在沙堆」裡。他又說，特首林鄭月娥拒絕封關，是忽視基本法賦予特區政府實行出入境管制措施的權利，認為政府應將市民健康置於首位。<br />\n<br />\n工黨張超雄說，市面口罩價格急升，政府應為弱勢社群提供免費口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504826-20200125.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504826-20200125.htm&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=d52f201b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1504826-20200125.htm&h=70b5c13a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1504826-20200125.htm</a>"},{"pid":"784b14a2f90a1f4903c35874695fa5dd18212d89","tid":1842242,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T14:59:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"511befb718c7130dd9fcc42b360abe2d1383b743","tid":1842242,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:00:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c91df93e78be65e9496a4243bc4b3b219c8a78c1","tid":1842242,"uid":210895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:00:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecd2abae3332790fd1657f18c3e294f34f6166e6","tid":1842242,"uid":168020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T15:04:55.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}